---
---

<div>
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="eyebrow">What you'll practice</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      The skills between writing code and shipping on a team
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Every lab targets the execution skills that real teams evaluate — the ones no course covers.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto divide-y divide-[var(--color-border-subtle)]">
    <div class="content-list-item flex gap-5 text-left">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Code quality and standards</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">Write code that passes review: clean structure, clear naming, and patterns your team can maintain.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-list-item flex gap-5 text-left">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M23.546 10.93L13.067.452c-.604-.603-1.582-.603-2.188 0L8.708 2.627l2.76 2.76c.645-.215 1.379-.07 1.889.441.516.515.658 1.258.438 1.9l2.658 2.66c.643-.223 1.387-.078 1.9.435.721.72.72 1.896 0 2.614-.719.721-1.881.721-2.6 0-.539-.541-.674-1.337-.404-2.007L12.86 8.955v6.525c.176.086.342.203.488.348.713.721.713 1.883 0 2.6-.719.721-1.889.721-2.609 0-.719-.719-.719-1.879 0-2.598.182-.18.387-.316.605-.406V8.835c-.217-.091-.424-.222-.6-.401-.545-.545-.676-1.342-.403-2.009L7.636 3.7.45 10.881c-.6.605-.6 1.584 0 2.189l10.48 10.477c.604.604 1.582.604 2.186 0l10.43-10.43c.605-.603.605-1.582 0-2.187"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Git and pull requests</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">Branch safely, open clear PRs, and merge confidently after feedback.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-list-item flex gap-5 text-left">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Sprint execution</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">Break down tasks, report progress, and deliver in iterative cycles.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-list-item flex gap-5 text-left">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Testing and debugging</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">Find root causes fast, validate fixes, and avoid fragile releases.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-list-item flex gap-5 text-left">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 10.607z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">AI-assisted development</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">Use AI tools to move fast, review what they produce critically, and own every line that ships. Pro labs teach you to evaluate, refactor, and defend AI-generated code — the skill every team now expects.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-list-item flex gap-5 text-left">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Team communication</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">Write standup updates, log blockers, respond to review comments, and communicate decisions like a teammate.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
